[0.019, "o", "○ libvirtd.service - libvirt legacy monolithic daemon\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://laptopserver/usr/lib/systemd/system/libvirtd.service\u001b\\/usr/lib/systemd/system/libvirtd.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n    Drop-In: /usr/lib/systemd/system/libvirtd.service.d\r\n             └─\u001b]8;;file://laptopserver/usr/lib/systemd/system/libvirtd.service.d/10-secret.conf\u001b\\10-secret.conf\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n             /etc/systemd/system/libvirtd.service.d\r\n             └─\u001b]8;;file://laptopserver/etc/systemd/system/libvirtd.service.d/override.conf\u001b\\override.conf\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n     Active: inactive (dead)\r\nTriggeredBy: \u001b[0;1;32m●\u001b[0m libvirtd-admin.socket\r\n             \u001b[0;1;32m●\u001b[0m libvirtd.socket\r\n             \u001b[0;1;32m●\u001b[0m libvirtd-ro.socket\r\n       Docs: \u001b]8;;man:libvirtd(8)\u001b\\man:libvirtd(8)\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n             \u001b]8;;https://libvirt.org/\u001b\\https://libvirt.org/\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n\r\nJul 02 20:06:05 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mDependency failed for libvirt legacy monolithic daemon.\u001b[0m\r\nJul 02 20:06:05 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39mlibvirtd.service: Job libvirtd.service/start failed with result 'dependency'.\u001b[0m\r\nJul 02 20:06:41 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mDependency failed for libvirt legacy monolithic daemon.\u001b[0m\r\nJul 02 20:06:41 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;31m\u001b[0;1;39mlibvirtd.service: Job libvirtd.service/start failed with result 'dependency'.\u001b[0m\r\nJul 02 20:08:28 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185m\u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;1;38:5:185mDependency failed for libvirt legacy monolithic daemon.\u001b[0m\r\nJul 02 20:08:28 laptopserver systemd[1]: \u001b[0;1;39m\u001b[0;